---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="Privacy Policy | Hustlers University UK"
  description="Privacy Policy explaining how Hustlers University UK collects and uses information."
>
  <main class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-6 py-24 text-sm leading-relaxed text-[var(--color-text-muted)]">

    <h1 class="mb-2 text-2xl font-semibold text-[var(--color-text-light)]">
      Privacy Policy
    </h1>

    <p class="mb-8 text-xs opacity-70">
      Last updated: 9 September 2025
    </p>

    <p class="mb-6">
      This Privacy Policy explains how Hustlers University UK ("we", "us", "our") collects
      and uses information when you visit
      <a
        href="https://hustlersuniversity.uk"
        class="text-[var(--color-orange)] hover:underline"
      >
        hustlersuniversity.uk
      </a>.
    </p>

    <h2 class="mt-10 mb-3 text-lg font-semibold text-[var(--color-text-light)]">
      1) Who we are
    </h2>
    <p>
      Hustlers University UK operates this marketing website. We do not run the education
      platform or process platform memberships or payments. Platform subscriptions and
      account data are handled by the official provider linked from our site.
    </p>

    <h2 class="mt-10 mb-3 text-lg font-semibold text-[var(--color-text-light)]">
      2) What we collect
    </h2>
    <ul class="ml-4 list-disc space-y-2">
      <li>
        Contact details you submit (e.g., name, email, phone) via forms for callbacks or
        consultations.
      </li>
      <li>
        Usage data from analytics (page views, referrers, device information). This data is
        aggregated and not used to identify you personally.
      </li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="mt-10 mb-3 text-lg font-semibold text-[var(--color-text-light)]">
      3) How we use your information
    </h2>
    <ul class="ml-4 list-disc space-y-2">
      <li>To respond to your enquiries and provide requested information.</li>
      <li>To schedule and follow up on consultations.</li>
      <li>To analyse site performance and improve content.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="mt-10 mb-3 text-lg font-semibold text-[var(--color-text-light)]">
      4) Cookies &amp; analytics
    </h2>
    <p>
      We may use privacy-friendly analytics and standard cookies to understand basic site
      usage (such as which pages are visited). You can disable cookies in your browser at
      any time.
    </p>

    <h2 class="mt-10 mb-3 text-lg font-semibold text-[var(--color-text-light)]">
      5) Third-party links
    </h2>
    <p>
      Our website links to external services (including the official platform and checkout).
      Those sites have their own privacy policies which you should review separately. We do
      not control their data practices.
    </p>

    <h2 class="mt-10 mb-3 text-lg font-semibold text-[var(--color-text-light)]">
      6) Data retention &amp; security
    </h2>
    <p>
      Contact details submitted via our forms are kept only as long as necessary to respond
      to your request or as required by law. We implement reasonable technical and
      organisational measures to protect your information.
    </p>

    <h2 class="mt-10 mb-3 text-lg font-semibold text-[var(--color-text-light)]">
      7) Your rights (UK / EEA)
    </h2>
    <p>
      You may request access to, correction of, or deletion of personal data you have
      submitted via this website. To exercise your rights, contact us using the details
      below.
    </p>

    <h2 class="mt-10 mb-3 text-lg font-semibold text-[var(--color-text-light)]">
      8) Children
    </h2>
    <p>
      Our website is not directed to individuals under the age of 13, and we do not
      knowingly collect personal data from children.
    </p>

    <h2 class="mt-10 mb-3 text-lg font-semibold text-[var(--color-text-light)]">
      9) Changes to this policy
    </h2>
    <p>
      We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. The most current version will
      always be posted on this page.
    </p>

    <h2 class="mt-10 mb-3 text-lg font-semibold text-[var(--color-text-light)]">
      10) Contact
    </h2>
    <p>
      If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at
      <a
        href="mailto:support@hustlersuniversity.uk"
        class="text-[var(--color-orange)] hover:underline"
      >
        support@hustlersuniversity.uk
      </a>.
    </p>

    <p class="mt-16 text-xs opacity-70">
      Â© 2025 Hustlers University UK. All rights reserved.
    </p>

  </main>
</Layout>